MyBroadband has received Telkom’s Black Friday 2018 deals brochure, which features a range of smartphone deals. Telkom said that the deals will be available from 23-26 November 2018 or while stocks last. The company added that customers can also receive 60GB or 120GB of free Telkom data with the deals, along with additional bonus monthly data allocations. A selection of Telkom’s Black Friday deals are listed below. To see all the deals when the sale goes live, you can visit Telkom’s website.      